{"id": "1325369710019346493", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "懂了 所以那個毆打校貓的功能一定要製作出來\n~~畢竟打是情罵是愛 越打越愛 想必毆打功能一開肯定能夠兩天內超越目光擊殺量~~", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T07:46:03.047000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "6️⃣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 28}, {"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 13}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1325370123254763562", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "855461987805822987", "author_name": "shchng.", "author_bot": false, "content": "真希望這裡每天都有新東西", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T07:47:41.570000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1325370585240305705", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "但我還是希望如果要發那種像是+20之類的東西 麻煩先想一想玩家能不能接受 \n如果用膝蓋想都知道絕對會被噴 那就不要用前瞻這種感覺讓人以為要變成這樣子做的預告 會讓玩家產生極大的不安\n~~如果這是要做給資方看得話當我沒說~~", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T07:49:31.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 17}, {"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1325370752928845914", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "看到這破碎的文法就能知道校貓這次是真心的說話，而不是內部的社區管理策略，真讓我感動", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T07:50:11.696000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 24}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1325371678339104828", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "1156423870379741244", "author_name": "kong760", "author_bot": false, "content": "好啦老實說罵歸罵\n錯誤的部分其實有傾聽玩家建議修正就好\n我相信大部分玩家還是因為喜歡這個作品才會願意上來罵或者說建議~~但可能情緒影響措辭比較激烈~~\n如果不喜歡早就跑路退遊退群了\n也很高興貓還願意溝通而不是像大部分遊戲的策劃神隱打太極\n只是希望之後的方式可以再圓融一些啦 嗯嗯\n這樣社群跟遊戲整體體驗才會有所提升嘛\n~~阿有沒有特別做pv預告校貓活動等不及了😈~~", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T07:53:52.331000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1325371924016136296", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "1184260881010405386", "author_name": "chenyu3141", "author_bot": false, "content": "無限期支持貓貓，人非聖賢，貓貓貴在真實不做作，一味的官腔官調也應該不是大家想看到的製作人風格，作為一個忘卻玩家，我覺得該謝謝貓貓和製作組一直以來的辛勤付出", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T07:54:50.905000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "🤡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
