{"id": "1325374048531906570", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "711586313555410945", "author_name": "35sui", "author_bot": false, "content": "還是很期待貓貓在社群和玩家聊天的，對貓貓是又愛又恨的複雜糾葛，千言萬語都比不過擼貓好啊！相信大部分玩家不是討厭，是愛貓的表現！擼貓擼起來！", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T08:03:17.429000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-01-05T08:03:31.444000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
