{"id": "1325397064175194164", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "他的道歉一直都很誠懇\n他每次做了一些我們不能接受的事情的時候\n他的道歉都會讓我們覺得\n他下次不會再這麼幹\n\n但是每次、他下次就又這麼幹了，又這麼幹了。", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T09:34:44.786000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-01-05T09:34:55.114000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😂", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}, {"emoji": "🫠", "emoji_id": null, "count": 17}, {"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
