{"id": "1325420199977029642", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "557599119401811978", "author_name": "heikwok", "author_bot": false, "content": "要不要考慮星辰篇的環境跟融災的互換，10算10牌的常駐環境相比新融災的4條好像苛刻太多了", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T11:06:40.791000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1325422541476593686", "channel_id": "1325366151651524608", "type": 0, "author_id": "1287351071693606924", "author_name": "tururu_37124", "author_bot": false, "content": "就事论事，我进DC之后的观感其实猫猫除了爱踢人（现在这个改了就很好<:OK:1243504694312173588> ）没什么问题，至于圣杯节奏只能说确实大家没掌握分寸了<:nomoney:1243502188471517235>", "timestamp": "2025-01-05T11:15:59.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1325366151651524608", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "校猫碎碎念#自我风评反思", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
